| SGIE1 | VehicleMakeNet 105c (224×224) | `agent-cars-edge-ai` | `agent-ml-experimenter` |
| SGIE2 | VehicleTypeNet 6c | `agent-cars-edge-ai` | — (pretrained) |
| SGIE3 | LPDNet | `agent-cars-edge-ai` | — (pretrained) |
| SGIE4 | FaceDetect | `agent-cars-edge-ai` | — (pretrained) |
| OCR | LPR_STN (188×48, ONNX) | `agent-cars-python-backend` | — |
